{
  "id": "adv_card_kkr_03_02",
  "title": "赤崎こころ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "さて、こころはあれからどうなったかな……ん？",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "リズノワらしいバレンタイン……\n今までのバレンタインソングとは違うものを……",
      "startTime": 9.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "もの凄い勢いでメモしてるな……\nこれは邪魔をしない方がいいか",
      "startTime": 16.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ……あ、{user}さ～ん！\nどうしたんですか、そんなに私を熱心に見つめて～",
      "startTime": 28.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "……はっ！\nまさか、美少女アイドルに禁断の恋心を……！？",
      "startTime": 34.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "違う違う、あまりに集中してるから\n話し掛けない方がいいかなと思ったんだ",
      "startTime": 41.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "すっかり元気になってて、安心したよ",
      "startTime": 44.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "あ～……その件については、お世話になりました～",
      "startTime": 47.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "あの後ですね、愛ちゃんに暴力を振るわれまして\n……しくしく",
      "startTime": 57.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "おいおい、どうしてそうなるんだ！？",
      "startTime": 59.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、びっくりはしましたけど\nあれくらいへっちゃらですよ～",
      "startTime": 64.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "愛ちゃんは葵さんの指示でやったらしいんですよ",
      "startTime": 66.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、「あんなの冗談に決まってるじゃないか」\nって葵さんに言われたんですけどね～",
      "startTime": 74.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "愛ちゃんてばすっかり真に受けちゃったみたいで……\n大慌てで謝ってきましたよ～",
      "startTime": 80.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "はは、なんにせよ仲直り出来たみたいで良かったよ",
      "startTime": 83.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "今は愛ちゃんと、改めて曲のコンセプトを作ってます！\nでも今は愛ちゃんがソロのお仕事でいないんですよね～",
      "startTime": 92.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ、{user}さん\n暇ならちょっと付き合ってもらってもいいですか？",
      "startTime": 99.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "曲のイメージを作る上で、男性目線のお話を\n聞いたら参考になるかもしれないので～",
      "startTime": 105.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、大丈夫だよ\n夜の打ち合わせまでは空いてるから",
      "startTime": 110.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ早速ですけど、{user}さんは\nバレンタインにどんなイメージを持ってます？",
      "startTime": 116.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "女性が……気になってる男性にチョコを……的な？",
      "startTime": 119.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02-kkr014.m4a",
      "text": "かー！　甘い！　甘々ですね！",
      "startTime": 126,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02-kkr015.m4a",
      "text": "もっとこう大人というか、普通のバレンタインソングと\n違う雰囲気にしたいんですよ！",
      "startTime": 134.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02-kkr016.m4a",
      "text": "まあいいです。それじゃあ次は……\n女の子がチョコを渡すシチュエーションについてです！",
      "startTime": 141.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02-kkr017.m4a",
      "text": "愛ちゃんと相談したんですけど……これがまた酷くて",
      "startTime": 145.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02-kkr018.m4a",
      "text": "一緒にラーメンを食べた後に\n「デザートに……これどうかな？」とか",
      "startTime": 152.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02-kkr019.m4a",
      "text": "限界までトレーニングした後に\n「糖分補給に……これ、どうかな？」とか……",
      "startTime": 160.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "愛らしいというかなんというか……\nこころはどういうシチュエーションを考えてるんだ？",
      "startTime": 168.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02-kkr020.m4a",
      "text": "こころはオーソドックスに、男の子を呼び出しますね\nそして……こほんこほん",
      "startTime": 176.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02-kkr021.m4a",
      "text": "あの……これ、作ってきたんです\n受け取って……くれますか？",
      "startTime": 185.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02-kkr022.m4a",
      "text": "……って感じですかね～",
      "startTime": 189.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "おぉ……いいんじゃないか？　可愛いと思うぞ",
      "startTime": 191.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02-kkr023.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、でも、これがリズノワの雰囲気に\n合ってるかっていうと微妙なんですよね～",
      "startTime": 198.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02-kkr024.m4a",
      "text": "たとえば、莉央さんがさっきみたいな感じで\nチョコを渡してきたらどう思います？",
      "startTime": 204.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02-kkr025.m4a",
      "text": "照れながら、上目遣いで、おずおずと！",
      "startTime": 207.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "え、莉央さんが？　……あー……",
      "startTime": 211.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02-kkr026.m4a",
      "text": "……今、「ちょっといいかも」って思いましたね？",
      "startTime": 217.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "い、いや、そんなことは……",
      "startTime": 221.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_02-kkr027.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、想像してみたら意外と破壊力がありますね",
      "startTime": 223.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
